<view class="page">

<view class="hero">
  <image class="hero-bg" src="/images/background/0043.jpg" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="mask"></view>
  <view class="seal">膳</view>
  <view class="title">日日有膳</view>
  <view class="subtitle">顺应四时 · 好好吃饭</view>
</view>

<view class="card">
  <view class="season-header">
    <text class="season-name">今日 · 芒种</text>
    <text class="season-time">6月5日-6月21日</text>
  </view>
  <view class="season-text">
    仲夏将至，宜养脾胃，
    慎食生冷。
    湿热渐盛，
    宜清淡饮食。
  </view>
  <view class="line"></view>
  <view class="food-box">
    <view class="food-left">
      <view class="food-title green">今日宜食</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 山药</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 莲子</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 小米粥</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 冬瓜</view>
    </view>
    <view class="food-right">
      <view class="food-title red">今日少食</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 辛辣</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 油炸</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 冷饮</view>
      <view class="food-item">● 过饱</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="card">
  <view class="module-title">四时养生小笺</view>
  <view class="quote">
    芒种时节，仲夏将至。
    养生之道，
    贵在顺时而行，
    食疗为先。
  </view>
</view>

<view class="card">
  <view class="module-title">每日签语</view>
  <view class="bookmark">
    <view class="bookmark-text">{{dailyQuote}}</view>
    <view class="bookmark-author" wx:if="{{quoteAuthor}}">—— {{quoteAuthor}}</view>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="card">
  <image class="food-image" src="/images/background/01051.jpg" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="img-desc">山药莲子小米粥 · 宋代工笔意境</view>
</view>

<button class="btn" bindtap="goToResult">生成今日膳食</button>

<view class="footer">
  日日有膳
  <view>顺应四时 · 好好吃饭</view>
</view>

<!-- 隐私政策链接 -->
<view class="privacy-link" bindtap="goToPrivacy">隐私政策</view>

</view>